messages.content: Dulci’s mindscape gains a gentle blanket of snow as Rodophis and Ro2 enter.
( @Pastel warrior of hope!!! )
Her mindscape resembles a room! Her ideal room that opens up to a world of candy trees and a beautiful sky
“Wow...” both of them say together.
Dulci hums a bit "The candy trees are edible!"
“Oh, really? Then...do you mind if I...?”
"Go ahead!"
“O-OK!” Both Of them pull leaves from the candy tree. Notably, Ro2 has a bit less of a struggle.
“Damn...” Rodo says under her breath.
Dul2i goes over and takes a stick and noms it
Both Rodos see this and begin nomming as well. Rodo leans onto Dulci as she does so.
Dulci hummed
“They’re so cute...” Ro2 chuckled.
Dul2i nodded "Yeah~" She goes back to nibbling the others neck

Ro2 laughed. “I take it I’m the best sweet of all~”
Rodo can’t believe what she just heard.

"Mmhm~" She moves her nibbling down a bit

Dulci is trying to ignore them, shes so embarrassed

“Then go ahead, nibble all you want~”
“I-what-?!” Rodo is at a loss for words.
Then, Ro2 takes her hair out of its ponytail holder.
She moves down to nibble her shoulder a bit
“D-Damn, that’s...kinda hot...”
Dulci is just hiding in one of the trees now...shes so embarrassed

“Oh, what’s the matter? Can’t handle a little teasing?”
“You’re making all of this so **sexy**!”
Dul2i decides to pin Ro2 down

“What the-?!” Rodo gasps. 
Ro2 laughs, giving that dark growl again. “We’re going there, huh?”
She giggled and leans against her neck  purring loudly
“Oh, by the Stars...I love you so much.” She purred back, kissing her neck.

Theres a _very_ loud squeak from Dulci....Shes so red.

"Mmm this is fun~"
@Gekitoutsu Rispba
"I know~" Ro2 wrapped her tail around Dul2i's.
"Rodo why dont you go climb the tree and get Dulci~? Pretty sure she would love that~" Dul2i giggled a bit
"I don't see any more of us." Ro2 laughed.

Dulci is just hiding in the tree, a mad blush on her face

"Go on~" She whispers in Rodos ear something "Call her your princess~ Shes always wanted to be called that~"
Rodo's face is bright red, but slowly she starts climbing up.
Dulci is just trying to hide her face
"M-Mind if I join you...ᵖʳᶦⁿᶜᵉˢˢ...?"
Dulci squeaked but made room for her "Y-Ye-yeah......"
She scooted in next to her, face pale white.
Her tail wrapped around the others
"I...I can't believe I said that..." She muttered.
"S-said what....?" She tilted her head
“C-Called you Princess...”
"W-well.....I-I dont mind...."
“...The other you said...you *wanted* to be called that...”
She blushed more ".....Y-Yeah.....C-Cause.....your like my knight....."
“R-Really...?”
She nodded and scooted closer to her

“Well...that’s nice...” Rodo said quietly. 
“I’ll remember that, my lady.” Ro2 smiled.

She gently kissed her cheek before looking away 

"Aww shes embarrassed~! How cute~!" Dul2i giggled
"She's adorable when she's flustered~" Ro2 laughed.
Rodo just looked down, face white as snow.
"I-I, uh...I guess I think that...?"
Dulci is so red
"Oh, my *god*, why are you guys like this? Is your whole purpose to embarrass us?!"
( @Pastel warrior of hope!!! )

"We are only what you guys wanna be~" Dul2i giggled "I represent Dulcis more...hm....naughty side that she keeps hidden~!"

Ducli whimpered a bit and looked away from Rodo. Her secret was out to her girlfriend....
"Naughty?!" Rodo gasped, more shocked than anything.
"Mmhm~ Theres one timeline where she was dating a vampire named Jen~ That time spent with her influenced her to try new things and well~ She liked it!" Dul2i giggled
Rodo looked angry at first, but then her anger subsided. Of *course* there were going to be timelines where they hadn't met.
"New things, huh?" Ro2 asked.
Dul2i suddenly dissapeared. Dulci willed her away. She...was snifing a bit
Ro2 disappeared shortly after.
"D-Dulci...?" Rodo looked over at her.
"I-Im sorry......" She whimpered
"...Look, if it's about Jen...i-it's fine."
"A-About what Ive kept from you.....I keep uo this sweet innocent act cause Im scared if I act any other way you wont like me anymore....." She sniffled
"Wh- What are you talking about? I-I'd love you no matter what..."
"Y-You.....You will....?" Her wings fluttered a bit
"Of course!" She nodded.
She smiled and wiped her tears away and hugged her
She hugged her back. "I love you...sweetie."
"I love you too my Blueberry~" Shes purring now
She purred back, gently.
She was so happy now
"I-I'm...glad to see you're feeling better..."
"Mmmm I think its better without the other 2 around for now...." She purred
"I agree...I think we know enough about each other to be all right."
She nodded
She purred, wrapping her tail around hers.
